    "body": "### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ spack install fontconfig@2.12.3%gcc8.3.1 arch=linux-rhel7-broadwell\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Information on your system\r\n\r\n* **Spack:** 0.16.1-2245-4cca69f4ed\r\n* **Python:** 3.7.2\r\n* **Platform:** linux-rhel7-broadwell\r\n* **Concretizer:** clingo\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\n\r\nThis is a known issue with tarballs.  Refer to https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/fontconfig/fontconfig/-/issues/10 for more information about the work-around.\r\n\r\n### General information\r\n\r\n- [x] I have run `spack debug report` and reported the version of Spack/Python/Platform\r\n- [x] I have run `spack maintainers <name-of-the-package>` and @mentioned any maintainers\r\n- [ ] I have uploaded the build log and environment files\r\n- [x] I have searched the issues of this repo and believe this is not a duplicate\r\n",
